name: FAngelscriptInputBindData
doc: It's a shame we have to wrap. But it's not a hot path, and it's better than doing an engine mod. Best would of course be if AS type binds were made aware to UHT so binding worked here.

ConfirmTargetCommand: Defines command string that will be bound to Confirm Targeting
CancelTargetCommand: Defines command string that will be bound to Cancel Targeting
EnumName: Returns enum to use for ability binds. E.g., "Ability1"-"Ability9" input commands will be bound to ability activations inside the AbiltiySystemComponent
ConfirmTargetInputID: If >=0, Confirm is bound to an entry in the enum
CancelTargetInputID: If >=0, Cancel is bound to an entry in the enum
